00:13:13.320 --> 00:13:13.960
Tracy.

00:13:14.200 --> 00:13:15.399
Somos ambos adultos aqui.

00:13:15.759 --> 00:13:16.960
Deixe de ser infantil.

00:13:17.200 --> 00:13:18.200
Sabe muito bem

00:13:18.240 --> 00:13:19.840
