00:14:32.679 --> 00:14:33.559
maquilhagem,

00:14:34.279 --> 00:14:35.480
e sem obsessão

00:14:36.519 --> 00:14:38.399
sobre a compra de artigos com desconto.

00:14:41.919 --> 00:14:43.440
Quando namorava com ele,

00:14:45.440 --> 00:14:46.559
Quase me esquecia.

00:14:47.720 --> 00:14:48.360
